.TH manta-get-groups 1  "groups " 
.SH NAME
manta\-get\-groups \- List node groups visible to your token (or look up one by name)
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBmanta get groups\fR [\fB\-o\fR|\fB\-\-output\fR] [\fB\-h\fR|\fB\-\-help\fR] [\fIGROUP_NAME\fR] 
.SH DESCRIPTION
List node groups visible to your token (or look up one by name)
.SH OPTIONS
