\fB\-o\fR, \fB\-\-output\fR \fI<FORMAT>\fR [default: table]
Output format
.br

.br
\fIPossible values:\fR
.RS 14
.IP \(bu 2
json
.IP \(bu 2
table
.RE
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
Print help
.TP
[\fIGROUP_NAME\fR]
